Odoo All In One Product Image Display

Display product quantities in an alternative unit of measure across products, sale orders, deliveries, purchase orders, and invoices.

How it Works? click hear to watch video

FEATURES

Display product quantities in primary and secondary units across all modules.
Choose a secondary unit, like grams (gm) or milligrams (mg), for flexibility.
Real-time updates ensure accurate quantities in all transactions.
Improves accuracy and clarity by offering multiple unit options.
User-friendly interface for selecting and viewing alternative units.
Seamless integration with Odoos core modules for easy use.

What is the Odoo All-in-One Unit of Measure app?

  • The Odoo All-in-One Unit of Measure app allows users to display product quantities in both primary and secondary units across multiple Odoo modules, including products, sale orders, deliveries, purchase orders, and invoices.

What is the Odoo All-in-One Unit of Measure app?

  • The Odoo All-in-One Unit of Measure app allows users to display product quantities in both primary and secondary units across multiple Odoo modules, including products, sale orders, deliveries, purchase orders, and invoices.
